{"tid":1378939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝衝衝！衝有用咩？","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:14:59.000Z","uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f93bbe211d617c1fc50f7db8d84a4f150d9e5268","tid":1378939,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"邊個話勇武一定要衝<br />\n<br />\n話說14年旺角鳩嗚嘅時候，有條女用津路掉個差佬，一想捉佢就即刻尖叫，縮返去一堆男人後面，之後順住人流走左了，而現場啲男人又真係乜都冇做，個差佬勁撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解鬼佬連農場係用噴漆唔係用memo紙？<br />\n因為高效率呀，噴一噴就成幅牆人哋又難清<br />\n同理，點解人地革命係用磚頭係用火？<br />\n因為係暴徒呀，岀黎搗亂，係俾人捉果個呀<br />\n<br />\n緊係拉遠距離打啦，弓又好繩套住重物投擲又好<br />\n射完就走<br />\n<br />\n點都好過拎住防具衝上前<br />\n又冇隊型，輸硬又容易俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n你唔主動攻擊，變左大量嘅人力成本只係用黎佔路，效率極低。<br />\n對方唔郁你冇得郁，行行企企唔知做乜，相信好多前線都經歷過。一分散左就更危險，落單俾人捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人慣左砌路障<br />\n然後拎住遮排排企，又冇遠攻喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係前面總有啲人<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">型左膠</span>話「好危險呀<br />\n一陣前面退唔到呀」要拆少少你個路障<br />\n變左跟本防到車防唔到人，咁辛苦起岀黎，人地用刀仔就拆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後整路障，應該路中心堆座山岀黎，點火<br />\n咁就癱瘓左條路，咁熱你叫狗仔點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>［領取新手村武器］</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRzDMCVdPwnE&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1hCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=39e846ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE</a>"},{"pid":"a3d191750315401cda3a781ea2ab477423aa5ed5","tid":1378939,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2571777543580922a8f76c1fda00c57f2716e8","tid":1378939,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n遠攻<br />\n甚至拎主動權突擊"},{"pid":"59560c8537fe98c53a35690dbe5d3da87914f89b","tid":1378939,"uid":86109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}